	(text_box "This subsystem interfaces with a micro/mini servo where the internal control board has been removed.\n\nRequired Servo Modifications:\n\nThe user must expose the following internal wires:\n\n  • DC Motor Terminals: MOT_A, MOT_B.\n  • Feedback Potentiometer: +3V3, POT (wiper), GND.\n\nConnection Options:\n\nFor convenience, the user can utilize either:\n\n  • JST-PH 5P Horizontal Connector (J4).\n  • 2.54mm 2x3P Pin Header (J5).\n\nServo Sensors:\n\n  • Potentiometer / Position Sensor with filtering.\n  • Onboard / External Temperature Sensor.\n  • Motor Encoder Connector ( future expansion ).\n\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 203.2 27.94 0)
		(size 78.74 101.6)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
